Chmod Guide
0 - ---
1 - --x
2 - -w-
3 - -wx
4 - r--
5 - r-x
6 - rw-
7 - rwx
------------------------------------------------###------------------------------------
Just a note in DSM 6 to use:

Code: Select all
chmod -R 755 /volume1/homes/[username]


The -R is to make it recursive, in case you already created the keys before running the chmod.

----------------------------------------------####---------------------
